---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="How we collect and use information.">
  <section class="cba-legal">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="lede">This Privacy Policy explains how Catharsis Body Art ("we", "us") collects, uses, and safeguards information when you use our website and services.</p>

      <div class="legal-grid">
        <article class="legal-block">
          <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>We collect information you provide directly (e.g., contact details when submitting booking or contact forms) and limited technical data (e.g., basic analytics and cookies to improve site performance). We do not sell personal information.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-block">
          <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
          <p>We use your information to respond to inquiries, schedule appointments, manage events, improve the site, and communicate important updates. With your consent, we may send promotional messages which you can opt out of at any time.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-block">
          <h2>Sharing</h2>
          <p>We may share information with trusted providers who assist our operations (e.g., email, hosting, analytics). These providers are bound by confidentiality obligations and may only use data to fulfill their services.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-block">
          <h2>Cookies</h2>
          <p>We use cookies and similar technologies for essential functionality and analytics. You can control cookies via your browser settings. See our <a href="/cookies">Cookie Policy</a> for details.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-block">
          <h2>Data Security & Retention</h2>
          <p>We take reasonable measures to protect information from unauthorized access and retain data only as long as necessary for the purposes described.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-block">
          <h2>Your Choices</h2>
          <p>You can request access, correction, or deletion of your personal information by contacting us. We will respond consistent with applicable laws.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="legal-block">
          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>If you have questions about this policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@catharsisba.com">info@catharsisba.com</a> or (317) 286-7092.</p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-footer">
        <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/">Home</a>
        <span class="muted small">Updated {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

